{"tid":1178871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［逃犯條例] 中國法院係可以缺席審判 同有死刑","createTime":"2019-05-30T16:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T17:03:16.000Z","uid":54346,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b9bd5d074b37fb966f706ad5c7b3e435889ad87c","tid":1178871,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">經修改的《刑事訴訟法》，將「缺席審判程序」以專章的形式寫入。法條規定，對於「貪污賄賂犯罪」案件，以及需要及時審判，經由最高人民檢察院核准的「嚴重危害國家安全犯罪」「恐怖活動犯罪」案件，若嫌犯、被告在中國境外，經監察機關、公安機關移送起訴，而人民檢察院認為已經罪證確鑿、依法應當追究刑事責任者，可以向人民法院提起公訴。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nSource :[url]<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/107018?fbclid=IwAR3ZZgr7H0TOWyDrlBXcRF_emR_3uJTzjihxgnL5qIzri-l4GHTgGI-WWJk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F107018%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ZZgr7H0TOWyDrlBXcRF_emR_3uJTzjihxgnL5qIzri-l4GHTgGI-WWJk&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1TQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=27f62356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/107018?fbclid=IwAR3ZZgr7H0TOWyDrlBXcRF_emR_3uJTzjihxgnL5qIzri-l4GHTgGI-WWJk</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算你係香港 佢地可以係中國法院入你國家安全罪先之後 再拉你上去</span></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">\n中共有49項可以判你死刑 其中包括\n危害國家安全罪（7項）\t\n背叛國家罪\n分裂國家罪\n武裝叛亂、暴亂罪\n投敵叛變罪\n間諜罪\n為境外的機構、組織、人員竊取、刺探、收買、非法提供國家秘密或者情報罪\n資敵罪</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n如果你講錯少少野得罪當權者 佢地就可以用死刑黎威脅你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">話比身邊嘅人知<br />\n<br />\n六月九號 為自己 為之前為香港犧牲嘅義士 為香港<br />\n</span><br />\n企出黎！"},{"pid":"1335935b79021757d434bd7ce07def612140d7d8","tid":1178871,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdea696a3c3cc855fbeb87154ab91ec43424cb2","tid":1178871,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T17:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1e87b7bffe82855e54fdc66c64de5c4afe57c9","tid":1178871,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T17:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feddca680092f3140b008637d8eb668348ac9c4a","tid":1178871,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}